@startuml
title Agent Key 轮换（rotate-key）

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

<style>
  participant { Padding 28 }
  box { Padding 10 }
</style>

autonumber

actor "开发者" as Dev
participant "SDK" as SDK
participant "Vault" as Vault
participant "Registry" as Registry

== SDK 自动创建新 key ==

Dev -> SDK : rotate_key(new_key_name="agent-v2")
SDK -> Vault : 创建 ecdsa-p256 key + 读取公钥
Vault --> SDK : public_key_pem
SDK -> SDK : 构造新 signer + AgentKey


== 双签名 ==

SDK -> Vault : 新 key 签名 proof
Vault --> SDK : proof headers
SDK -> Vault : 旧 key 签名完整请求
Vault --> SDK : 签名 headers

== 提交 Registry ==

SDK -> Registry : POST /registry/agents/rotate-key\nAPI key + 旧签名 + proof
Registry -> Registry : 校验 developer + 旧签名 + proof\n+ owner + timestamp + nonce

alt 全部通过
    Registry --> SDK : 旧 key → inactive，新 key → active
    SDK -> SDK : 更新本地 kid / signer / metadata
    SDK --> Dev : 成功
else 失败
    Registry --> SDK : 拒绝（SIGNATURE_INVALID / OWNER_MISMATCH / ...）
    SDK --> Dev : 异常，本地状态不变
end

@enduml
